WEBVTT

00:11:56.495 --> 00:12:00.473
Na kumbuka - daima neema huja mwishoni.

00:12:01.652 --> 00:12:04.761
Eleven: Mungu anamaanisha wema tu.

00:12:04.785 --> 00:12:07.226
Hata haiogopeshi.

00:12:07.250 --> 00:12:11.700
Ina maana ya kimungu au upendo,
kimaarifa

00:12:11.724 --> 00:12:15.449
au, kama tulivyojifunza kutoka kwa "Deteriorata" mkuu

00:12:15.473 --> 00:12:17.081
"keki ya kikosmiki."

00:12:17.800 --> 00:12:20.719
Jina jema la Mungu ni: "Sio mimi."

00:12:21.827 --> 00:12:24.573
Emerson alisema mtu mwenye furaha zaidi duniani

00:12:24.597 --> 00:12:28.775
ni anayejifunza ibada kutoka kwa mazingira.

00:12:28.799 --> 00:12:31.925
Hivyo nenda nje na angalia juu.